    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieves level 2 against a required level 3 due to single-configuration testing; this shortfall is accepted given medium model risk, medium decision consequence, corroborating multi-laboratory experimental data, and quantitative output comparison results well within acceptance bounds (all E/uval < 1.0, all percent differences <3%). Overall credibility is sufficient to support regulatory submission for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct.",
